	(text_box "CC1000 All in one Transceiver 300MHz to 1 Ghz\n\n315 / 433 / 868 and 915 MHz\n\n• High sensitivity (typical -110 dBm at 2.4kBaud)\n• Programmable output power -20 to 10 dBm\n• Low supply voltage (2.1 V to 3.6 V) MAX 5V\n\nA ideia é Implementar para as 3 frequencias - 315 / 433 / 868\nO MCU controla qual com Switches?\n\nUsar o RSSI para adaptar o ganho?\n"
		(exclude_from_sim yes)
